      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For instance, SnapATAC2 took only 13.4 min to analyze a dataset with 200,000 cells, whereas PeakVI needed approximately 4 h... SnapATAC2 stood out by requiring only 21 GB of memory to process 200,000 cells.",
