      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "This strategy substantially shortens the time and space complexity, making it linearly proportional to the number of cells in the single-cell data... This method exhibits linear space and time usage relative to the input matrix size, resulting in a faster and memory-efficient approach for processing of large datasets.",
