      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SnapATAC2 is a comprehensive, high-performance solution for single-cell omics data analysis... The preprocessing module handles raw BAM files, assesses data quality, creates count matrices and spots doublets, ensuring a strong base for downstream analysis.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms SnapATAC2 handles BAM files, creates count matrices, and supports tile-based and peak-based matrices. However, the paper does not explicitly discuss iterative modification of count matrices or the preservation of fragment-level data in backed AnnData objects as a core workflow feature.",
