      "asbval:note": "Paper uses '10x PBMC 10k' (not explicitly 'pbmc10k_multiome') and multiple 10x Multiome datasets. The card references a specific dataset name that is semantically equivalent but not verbatim in the paper.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41592-023-02139-9",
