      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SnapATAC2 is a comprehensive, high-performance solution for single-cell omics data analysis... The core of SnapATAC2 is its embedding/clustering module, which introduces a new algorithm for reducing data dimensions... By adopting the AnnData format, it facilitates effortless integration with established packages like SCANPY, scvi-tools and SCENIC+.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms SnapATAC2 performs spectral embedding, clustering, and uses AnnData format for interoperability.",
