      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SnapATAC2 (version 2.3.1) is a Python package developed in this study. We used the 'snapatac2.tl.spectral' function to generate the lower-dimensional embedding of the data.",
      "asbval:note": "Version 2.3.1 is confirmed in the paper. The matrix-free spectral embedding algorithm (passages 3, 9) is described as 'specifically designed for cosine similarity,' confirming it as the default.",
