      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The core of SnapATAC2 is its embedding/clustering module, which introduces a new algorithm for reducing data dimensions. This module also helps in identifying unique cell clusters and revealing biological patterns.",
