      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SnapATAC2 is modular and adaptable, and allows users to tailor their analysis to specific requirements and integrate with other software packages from the scverse ecosystem, such as SCANPY and scvi-tools. By adopting the AnnData format, it facilitates effortless integration with established packages like SCANPY, scvi-tools and SCENIC+.",
