      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Linear dimensionality reduction algorithms, such as principal component analysis (PCA)... are popular due to their computational efficiency... However, these algorithms are not optimal for handling single-cell datasets with complex and nonlinear structures",
