      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The preprocessing module handles raw BAM files, assesses data quality, creates count matrices and spots doublets, ensuring a strong base for downstream analysis. The core of SnapATAC2 is its embedding/clustering module, which introduces a new algorithm for reducing data dimensions.",
